Class SubmitOnClickListener

java.lang.Object
  wogwt.translatable.http.Updater
      wogwt.translatable.http.SubmitUpdater
          wogwt.translatable.http.SubmitOnClickListener

public class SubmitOnClickListener
extends SubmitUpdater

Sends the all the form values to the server using the form action url and updates a DOM container with the response. This is intended to be attached to a WOSubmitButton element.
